      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDSTAR VOGUE (1) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (19.98) at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can atone. ATOMIC GHOST (5) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (20.13), beaten 4 lengths. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Leading player again. STRIKING TIDE (6) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (20.09) at this track in a Grade 6 over 352m. Has good speed so he should be prominent despite the draw. Will give a great sight again. ZORKA (2) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
